User Demographics 2

users2.Rd

A dataset with unique participant ID, birth year, and sex. To be used in conjunction with data from disgust, disgust_scores, personality, personality_scores, and users.

users2

Format

A data frame with 60000 rows and 3 variables:

user_id

Each participant's unique ID

birthyear

The participant's year of birth

sex

The participant's sex

Source

https://psyteachr.github.io/psyteachr/data/users2.csv
